<p>A <code>FiveFaceRatingPickerButton</code> is one face inside
  a <a href="/components/five-face-rating-picker/"><code>FiveFaceRatingPicker</code></a>.
  Each button is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  <code>data-value</code> (1–5). The example CSS renders an emoji
  per value: 😖 🙁 😐 🙂 😄.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/five-face-rating-picker/">Picker
  demo</a> for composed examples.</p>
